"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"[![Andre Cronje](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/2\\\\*Vjiwqoib1HcKLdkM1xwp_g.jpeg)](https://andrecronje.medium.com/?source=post_page-----abbc5f10e95a--------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*S0KBzzrlDLbHH\\\\_550d5Ohw.png)\\n\\nCrafting (I) has been released. These are regular goods, armor and weapons.\\n\\nEach crafting attempt costs 250xp per attempt, representing 1 day of effort.\\n\\nA crafter must have at least 1 skill point in Skills (Craft) to be able to attempt crafting.\\n\\nThe difficult class (DC) of crafting is based on the type of item.\\n\\nA crafter can craft;\\n\\n*   [Goods](https://ftmscan.com/address/0x0C5C1CC0A7AE65FE372fbb08FF16578De4b980f3#code) (DC 20)\\n*   [Armor](https://ftmscan.com/address/0xf5114A952Aca3e9055a52a87938efefc8BB7878C#code) (DC 20 + armor bonus)\\n*   [Weapons](https://ftmscan.com/address/0xeE1a2EA55945223404d73C0BbE57f540BBAAD0D8#code) (DC 20, DC 25, And DC 30 for Simple, Martial, and Exotic)\\n\\nThe craft check is calculated as follows;\\n\\n`1d20 + craft skill ranks + INT modifier`\\n\\nThe DC can be reduced by spending `craft (I) materials` which is farmable in The Cellar. The DC is decreased by 1 for each 10 `craft (I) materials` spent.\\n\\nShould a DC check be successful, materials worth the `cost` of the item will be used up to create the items. This is the cost in `gold`.\\n\\n**Technical**\\n\\nRarity Crafting: [0xf41270836dF4Db1D28F7fd0935270e3A603e78cC](https://ftmscan.com/address/0xf41270836df4db1d28f7fd0935270e3a603e78cc#code)\\n\\n`craft(summoner, base_type, item_type, crafting_materials)`\\n\\nHighly recommended to simulate an attempt first;\\n\\n`simulate(summoner, base_type, item_type, crafting_materials)`\\n\\nTo craft, you need to approve;\\n\\n*   `rarity.approve(_crafting_contract, summoner)`\\n*   `rarity_gold.approve(1758709, -1)`\\n*   `rarity_crafting_materials.approve(1758709, -1)` (optional if using crafting materials)\\n\\n**Socials**\\n\\n[Wiki](https://rarity.fandom.com/wiki/Rarity_Wiki)\\\\\\n[Github](https://github.com/andrecronje/rarity)\\\\\\n[Discord](https://discord.com/invite/F5URbkcvmD)\\n\\nWTB Longsword please ‚ù§\\n\",\"timestamp\":1634229209,\"title\":\"Rarity: Crafting - Andre Cronje - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"qcs78Pn5dOuVaqopN8rWEQucSBpeO1TsxUJ9E7ac4Uw\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x88d93ecff2B67ba407dB4A08E410647138FdeC4C\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"JMl1BQimX4KNhWnXoxk5EUUc9JEdX06N6hQmBNTBN6Q\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"NdqWL7yMTHiR2W6xXESHMMRVRaWLmwFi-MkR7VcEz8o\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"IVrkoLRhLqTdUC7uQqTenoDHc8rq5JJutw7HTg6J8izxuWYzxJEAla0I7FG3ov7265vTWjrL2EpOYW5W9bmtfA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x3e7be60dd545ad0eb0b1eefbbdb0a2fc228eec6d362dabab9c3bc5bc934390fe1f47be07b28b9b19443c03d3171b1337259e780777800f6d7fbd356fa794715d1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"JMl1BQimX4KNhWnXoxk5EUUc9JEdX06N6hQmBNTBN6Q\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"NdqWL7yMTHiR2W6xXESHMMRVRaWLmwFi-MkR7VcEz8o\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"qcs78Pn5dOuVaqopN8rWEQucSBpeO1TsxUJ9E7ac4Uw\"}"